sec.p:
Figure 1 illustrates and defines the features of the time evolution of the joint angles on which the analyses of the kinematics were based. Because systematic differences in coordination were present depending on whether peak flexion or peak extension was chosen as reference, the relative phase between the hands (Φ) was calculated for each cycle as 
